m\": 1149, \"to\": 1253, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1149, \"end\": 1155, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_men's_national_volleyball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999743704760254, \"rank\": 2.5627548666942924e-05, \"text\": \"Poland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_men's_national_volleyball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_men's_national_volleyball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Poland's biggest star Wilfredo Leon, who had 94 points in Paris, had a quiet game by his standards with just 9 points.\", \"from\": 1255, \"to\": 1373, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1255, \"end\": 1261, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_men's_national_volleyball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999743704760254, \"rank\": 2.5627548666942924e-05, \"text\": \"Poland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_men's_national_volleyball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_men's_national_volleyball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1277, \"end\": 1290, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wilfredo_Le\\u00f3n\", \"score\": 0.999999995579401, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Wilfredo Leon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q15117302\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wilfredo_Le\\u00f3n\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wilfredo_Le\\u00f3n\"}, {\"begin\": 1313, \"end\": 1318, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998076419, \"rank\": 1.9233032005864227e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The teams got off to a sizzling start with every spike and block drawing massive roars from a full house.\", \"from\": 1375, \"to\": 1480, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Poland fell behind in the opening set with several service errors before France wrapped it up when Patry made an excellent dig to set himself up for a devastating kill.\", \"from\": 1482, \"to\": 1650, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1482, \"end\": 1488, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_men's_national_volleyball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999743704760254, \"rank\": 2.5627548666942924e-05, \"text\": \"Poland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_men's_national_volleyball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_men's_national_volleyball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1555, \"end\": 1561, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9982956377477029, \"rank\": 0.00170376190907395, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Leon lifted Poland when he attacked with purpose until Brizard denied him a third straight point with the first block of the match, following it up with two more to give France the lead in the second.\", \"from\": 1652, \"to\": 1852, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1664, \"end\": 1670, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_men's_national_volleyball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999743704760254, \"rank\": 2.5627548666942924e-05, \"text\": \"Poland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_men's_national_volleyball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_men's_national_volleyball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1822, \"end\": 1828, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9982956377477029, \"rank\": 0.00170376190907395, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Clevenot's clever shot selection for France had been instrumental and he scored three in a row, winning a key battle at the net before sealing a 2-0 lead with a superb spike.\", \"from\": 1854, \"to\": 2028, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1891, \"end\": 1897, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9982956377477029, \"rank\": 0.00170376190907395, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Four monster blocks at the start of the third set the tone for France as things spun out of control for Poland.\", \"from\": 2030, \"to\": 2141, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2093, \"end\": 2099, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9982956377477029, \"rank\": 0.00170376190907395, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2134, \"end\": 2140, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_men's_national_volleyball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999743704760254, \"rank\": 2.5627548666942924e-05, \"text\": \"Poland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_men's_national_volleyball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_men's_national_volleyball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sensing a famous win, the home crowd once again got involved in a loud and proud rendition of La Marseillaise - the French anthem.\", \"from\": 2142, \"to\": 2272, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2258, \"end\": 2264, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.6174122105977436, \"rank\": 0.5801370659245064, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Poland saved four match points but only delayed the inevitable when Leon's serve went long to spark wild celebrations on the floor and in the stands.\", \"from\": 2274, \"to\": 2423, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2274, \"end\": 2280, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_men's_national_volleyball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999743704760254, \"rank\": 2.5627548666942924e-05, \"text\": \"Poland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_men's_national_volleyball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_men's_national_volleyball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Leon was disappointed with the silver but took pride in standing on the podium.\", \"from\": 2425, \"to\": 2504, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are happy, for a really long time we did not reach the podium at the Olympics,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2506, \"to\": 2598, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So I should be proud of the team.\", \"from\": 2599, \"to\": 2633, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"- Rappler.com  How does this make you feel?\", \"from\": 2633, \"to\": 2677, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"follow us\", \"from\": 2679, \"to\": 2688, \"entities\": []}]}"